column5: Hi all,  Have a stack of videos from last year to catch up on, my computer has been messing up since last summer and finally got round to fixing it, new SSD and upgraded to 24GB Ram....it screams now. So....here is a video from last fall, out for grouse and walleye at Lac Seul with my best pal Roloff.

Fish and birds in the same day. I wish.  I remember traveling those logging roads during the moose hunt. My pop would drive 100 kph to make the ride smooth over that wash board. I guess with the boat in tow, that wont be happening.
